Proposed Revision of Federal Information Processing Standards (FIPS) 119, ADA


<AGENCY>
AGENCY: 

National Institute of Standards and Technology (NIST), Commerce.


</AGENCY>
<ACTION>
ACTION: 

Notice; Request for comments.




