SHA-1 may also be used whenever it is necessary to generate a condensed version of a message. 

Implementations: The SHA-1 may be implemented in software, firmware, hardware, or any combination thereof.
Only implementations of the SHA-1 that are validated by NIST will be considered as complying with this standard.
Information about the requirements for validating implementations of this standard can be obtained from the National
