Except where duplication of allocation would result, each public body and cooperative within the marketing areas
as shown in Appendix A will be eligible for an allocation of existing power, except for the City of Oxford, Georgia.
No reallocation of existing power for the benefit of Oxford is proposed at this time. Existing preference customers
