The Department is also undertaking a comprehensive review of its Title III programs; therefore, changes in outcome
measures will be deferred until the results of this critical assessment are available. Governors will continue to
be required to set an entered employment rate standard for their Title III programs and are encouraged to establish
an average wage at placement goal. At the same time, the Department will be exploring ways to use performance standards
