Braidwood Unit 1 TS Amendment 50 imposed a 100 calendar days with T

hot

 greater than 500
 F operating limit on Unit 1. This limitation was a consequence of the amount of MSLB leakage predicted in Braidwood
Station's April 30, 1994, submittal. These predictions were made using the Log-Logistic method of draft NUREG 1477,
