July 1, 1994.



Pursuant to Section 19(b)(1) of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934 (``Exchange Act''), 15 U.S.C. 78s(b)(1), notice
is hereby given that on June 22, 1994, the National Association of Securities Dealers, Inc. (``NASD'' or ``Association''),
